<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人飞到了大唐上空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧流下了幸福的泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看到皇帝的宫殿了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们去送真经吧，我在这里等着你们。”门将说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧一行人落在地上，进入宫殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皇帝的眼睛亮了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“御弟！”他抱住了唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“数年来，我都在想是否还能再见到你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你真的取到真经了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”唐僧说，“但是，请原谅我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>取经时间比预想的要长。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不必道歉。”皇帝说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他注意到唐僧的徒弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走上前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是美猴王孙悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>曾经打败过整个天兵天将。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有我是猪八戒。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫沙悟净。”紫色和尚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“西天取经的路上，是他们保护我的。”唐僧解释道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有他们，我是到不了西天的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皇帝低头向悟空他们行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“您不必行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>能帮助师父，我们很高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗯……我和悟净是这样想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒一直抱怨来着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒哼了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，皇帝举行了盛宴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皇帝问了唐僧很多关于西天取经的问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他听了唐僧的故事，非常吃惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要盖一座壮观的塔。”皇帝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把真经放到那里，安全地保管。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把手放在唐僧的肩膀上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人们会永远记住你的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是你这位勇敢的和尚去西天取回了真经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>托你的福，我们百姓不用再受苦了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃完饭后，皇帝让唐僧念真经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧笑了。“我愿意给您念真经！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧坐在一个台子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>台子上的三个篮子里放有真经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打开一个卷轴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，金光充满整个屋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人升到了空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得回雷音寺了。”门将说，“佛祖在等你们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，走吧。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，师徒四人就又出现在佛祖面前，他们低头行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他的佛和菩萨站在佛祖身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖先跟马说：“你驮着唐僧来西天，你被宽恕了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你现在将成为天上的八部天龙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道光闪过，一条大金龙飞上了天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟净。”佛祖说，“你也被宽恕了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你现在将成为金身罗汉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净的身体变成了金色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他低头行礼。“谢谢，佛祖。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也被宽恕了，八戒。”佛祖说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你将成为净坛使者，来管理佛教祭坛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个职位非常重要。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒低头行礼。“谢谢，佛祖。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，佛祖看向唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“托你的福，东方百姓不会再受苦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你完成了一件别人无法做到的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在你成佛了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧低头向佛祖行礼，他的头上出现了一个光圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢，佛祖。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，佛祖看向悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有你，悟空。”他开始说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很久以前，你做了坏事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是那以后，你用自己的无边法力做了很多好事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>359285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你现在也成佛了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>359285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>367036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空低头行礼。“谢谢，佛祖。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>367036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>373785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦？”悟空突然觉得自己的头有点不一样了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>373785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>378111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“头箍消失了！”佛祖笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>378111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>381384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你再也不需要它了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>381384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>384284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和唐僧非常高兴，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>384284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>390786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和其他佛、菩萨站到了一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>390785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>404785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那以后，他们一直在西天生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>